Sentencas: In this work, we discuss ion conductive character of low-Y2O3-content yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) crystallized into high-symmetric phase (cubic and/or tetragonal phases) at relatively low temperature.
Titulo: Ion conductive character of low-yttria-content yttria-stabilized zirconia at low temperature

Sentencas: Low-Y2O3-content YSZ was certainly stabilized into high-symmetric phase by extreme thinning down to around 10 nm.
Titulo: Ion conductive character of low-yttria-content yttria-stabilized zirconia at low temperature

Sentencas: We analyzed the impedance response from ultra-thin YSZ films in metal/insulator/metal (MIM) capacitor measured in the temperature range of 30 degrees C-440 degrees C.
Titulo: Ion conductive character of low-yttria-content yttria-stabilized zirconia at low temperature

Sentencas: It is expected that a characteristic kink on Nyquist-diagram is correlated to the conductivity of inner grain of the YSZ.
Titulo: Ion conductive character of low-yttria-content yttria-stabilized zirconia at low temperature

Sentencas: The activation energy for ion conduction is monotonically reduced with decreasing Y2O3 content, whereas the conductivity still exhibits the highest value at certain Y2O3 content.
Titulo: Ion conductive character of low-yttria-content yttria-stabilized zirconia at low temperature
